{
  "stem": "3659.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yes, I would like to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was a very beautiful woman who enjoyed traveling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father enjoyed life very much, and so I guess he had a few girlfriends on the side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't have any problem not being able to afford them, and so he was able to afford that luxury.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were never made aware of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The home life was always-- you know, papa and mama were always there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know what went on behind the scenes, and we didn't realize it until later on in life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister may have been aware of it earlier than I was, because I didn't know it at the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so my mother enjoyed traveling, and she did a lot of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess she didn't want to be home that much to see, you know, of what.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also the home was taken care of because we were well taken care of, and so she didn't have to worry about that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And summer vacations were always-- my parents never spent their vacations together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father used to travel with his friends, and my mother traveled with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And usually we either rented a home somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It may have been in-- in Hungary on the-- on the-- what-- it was the Balaton.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we always rented something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she took the help with her, and we spent the summers away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We locked up the apartment, and we just went away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we came back, getting ready for school again and looking forward, especially my sister was already in dancing school, prior to Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so her social life started, and she had a-- she attended a ball.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
